flashCards.front: Explain the concept of 'game theory' in economics
flashCards.back: Game theory analyzes strategic interactions between rational decision-makers. It is used to understand behavior in competitive situations.

flashCards.front: Discuss the impact of social media on interpersonal relationships.
flashCards.back: Social media can both strengthen and strain interpersonal relationships. It provides connectivity but may also contribute to issues such as social comparison and cyberbullying.
